we can go home?

18:12.961 --> 18:16.791
'Cause my shoes are
still super-squishy.

18:16.921 --> 18:17.922
[giggling]

18:18.053 --> 18:19.620
Sure! Race you there!

18:19.750 --> 18:22.013
Ah! I knew
he'd say that.

18:22.144 --> 18:23.624
[laughter]

18:24.929 --> 18:26.844
Doodle, we're back!

18:26.975 --> 18:29.717
Sunny! Thank you,
thank you, thank you!

18:29.847 --> 18:30.935
[laughing]
You're welcome,

18:31.066 --> 18:32.676
you're welcome,
you're welcome!

18:32.807 --> 18:34.548
Uh, for what?

18:34.678 --> 18:35.810
For my new buddy,

18:35.940 --> 18:38.421
