and dance partner!

18:39.683 --> 18:40.684
[grunts]

18:40.815 --> 18:42.164
[laughing]

18:42.295 --> 18:44.514
[grunts]

18:44.645 --> 18:45.733
Ta-dah!

18:45.863 --> 18:47.822
Take a bow,
Sir Bearlington.

18:47.952 --> 18:49.780
Huh? That's not
Sir Bearlington.

18:51.608 --> 18:55.438
That's Teddy!
Hey, buddy!
Huh?

18:55.569 --> 18:56.744
[laughing]

18:56.874 --> 18:59.007
Wait.
He was here

18:59.138 --> 19:01.879
