19:08.190 --> 19:10.410
Where did you find
Junior's bear, Doodle?

19:10.540 --> 19:11.715
Junior's bear?

19:11.846 --> 19:13.891
[laughing]

19:14.022 --> 19:17.068
You mean...?
[sighs] Oh!

19:17.199 --> 19:19.070
He was in one of
the new supply boxes.

19:19.201 --> 19:21.899
I thought he was
a present for me.

19:22.030 --> 19:23.336
