tomorrow, huh?

19:25.816 --> 19:28.079
No, Doodle.
It's okay.

19:28.210 --> 19:30.343
You can keep him.

19:30.473 --> 19:32.432
[gasps]
Really?

19:32.562 --> 19:33.911
Yeah. Really?

19:34.042 --> 19:36.349
Uh-huh. I can
tell you love him

19:36.479 --> 19:37.872
as much as I do.

19:38.002 --> 19:39.090
Don't worry, Teddy.

19:39.221 --> 19:40.962
I'll still come
and visit.

19:41.092 --> 19:42.181
But now,
you and Doodle

19:42.311 --> 19:43.704
